No longer can our young peple depend on the coal mining industry for employment and must now seek other venues of occupation.
There is one well established industrial estate at Langthwaite Grange in{ South Kirkby}which affords some job opportunity. A further development is currently taking place at Dale Lane in{South Elmsall. These industrial estate developments are ascribed{development zones}funded by the {European Economic Community.}
Despite these recent developments there is much need for job creation in this community where there is an abundant workforce readily available.
